---
// Footer with contact form
---

<footer class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-white tracking-tight mb-6">Trabajemos juntos.</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 max-w-sm mb-8">
          Actualmente estoy disponible para proyectos freelance y abierto a oportunidades de tiempo completo.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@ivanmercedes.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white border-b border-white pb-1 hover:text-neutral-300 hover:border-neutral-300 transition-colors">
          hello@ivanmercedes.com <span class="iconify" data-icon="lucide:arrow-up-right" data-width="16"></span>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-neutral-900/30 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <form class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-neutral-500 mb-1.5">Nombre</label>
            <input type="text" class="w-full bg-neutral-950 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder-neutral-600 focus:outline-none focus:border-white/20 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-white/20 transition-all" placeholder="Juan Pérez" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-neutral-500 mb-1.5">Email</label>
            <input type="email" class="w-full bg-neutral-950 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder-neutral-600 focus:outline-none focus:border-white/20 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-white/20 transition-all" placeholder="juan@ejemplo.com" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-neutral-500 mb-1.5">Mensaje</label>
            <textarea class="w-full bg-neutral-950 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder-neutral-600 focus:outline-none focus:border-white/20 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-white/20 transition-all min-h-[100px]" placeholder="Cuéntame sobre tu proyecto..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-white text-black font-medium text-sm py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-200 transition-colors">
            Enviar Mensaje
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-neutral-600">
      <p>© 2024 Ivan Mercedes. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="https://twitter.com/ivanmercedes" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Twitter</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/ivanmercedes" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/ivanmercedes" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
